    was in some configurations setting CONFIG_HOTPLUG_CPU=y without asking,
    even when there was no actual requirement for CONFIG_HOTPLUG_CPU.
    This was triggered by SUSPEND_SMP that does a select HOTPLUG_CPU.
    
